text: CHBE-FM is a radio station in Victoria, British Columbia. It broadcasts at a frequency of 107.3 FM. The station was changed from 107.3 KOOL-FM to 107.3 Virgin Radio on February 8, 2019. ==References== == Other websites == *107.3 Virgin Radio Offical Website Category:Radio stations Category:Victoria, British Columbia
